    <releaseNotes>
Please note that this branch is depricated and will not be supported for long. 
Upgrade to &gt;= v2.0.0. See release notes for v2.0.0 for details.

## What's new?

### Orders:

- #3362: A new method, ListOrdersByEmail, has been added.  
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Orders/ListOrdersByEmail

- #2840: A new property, DropPoint has been added to Order.  
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Orders/Order  

### Shopping:

- #2840: Added support for external handling of delivery methods. A new method, UpdateDeliveryMethod4, has been added together with a new Entity for updating the delivery method, BasketDeliveryMethodUpdate.  
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Shopping/Checkout/UpdateDeliveryMethod4  
https://services.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Shopping/DeliveryMethods/BasketDeliveryMethodUpdate

## What's fixed?

### Products:

- #3380: Problem with variant unique texts on Product has been resolved.

### Shopping:

- #3361: Problem with deactivated promotions in checkout process has been resolved.

## Miscellaneous changes?

N/A

Regards, 

The Storm API Team
